♪ <i>Little crayons</i> ♪

535
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:15,759
♪ <i>Wrapped in pretty robes</i> ♪

536
00:32:15,759 --> 00:32:19,940
♪ <i>Red, yellow, blue, and green</i> ♪

537
00:32:20,580 --> 00:32:23,139
♪ <i>Little friends</i> ♪

538
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:25,519
♪ <i>Smiling happily</i> ♪

539
00:32:25,519 --> 00:32:29,220
♪ <i>Drawing a picture</i> ♪

540
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:32,939
♪ <i>Drawing birds</i> ♪

541
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:34,779
♪ <i>Soaring in the blue sky</i> ♪

542
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:37,720
Xiao Hu Lu. Your dad.

543
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:40,200
♪ <i>Sprouting in spring</i> ♪

544
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:42,639
♪ <i>You can draw the sun</i> ♪

545
00:32:42,639 --> 00:32:45,199
♪ <i>I'll draw the national flag</i> ♪

