♪ <i>We love you</i> ♪

548
00:32:50,239 --> 00:32:52,679
♪ <i>Motherland, motherland</i> ♪

549
00:32:52,679 --> 00:32:55,260
♪ <i>We love you</i> ♪

550
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:02,400
Do you want to stand in the center?

551
00:33:02,940 --> 00:33:05,700
But I think it's good to stand at the end.

552
00:33:05,700 --> 00:33:07,939
The center is the best place.

553
00:33:07,940 --> 00:33:10,179
I want to be the best.

554
00:33:10,180 --> 00:33:13,779
You're like me. You sing out of tune, so you may not get it.

555
00:33:13,779 --> 00:33:17,120
I know. I've been working hard.

556
00:33:22,300 --> 00:33:26,520
Dad, is it hard to sell your water purifiers?

557
00:33:27,380 --> 00:33:28,859
Someone will buy them.

558
00:33:28,860 --> 00:33:31,680
Dad, you should work hard too.

559
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:33,300
I will.

560
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:42,879
By the way, Dad, I'll tell you a secret.

561
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:44,819
What is it?

562
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:47,480
You can't be upset.

563
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,980
I won't.

564
00:33:49,620 --> 00:33:53,480
A guy is trying to woo my mom.

565
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:55,440
A guy?

566
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:02,519
Here, Xiaochun. Check it.

567
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:06,220
Don't worry.

568
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:09,340
I selected your products carefully.

569
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,899
I only deliver the best to you.

570
00:34:10,900 --> 00:34:13,600
Tell me if there are any problems.

571
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:17,960
Nice, not bad.

572
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,680
Unload them.

573
00:34:20,940 --> 00:34:24,080
By the way, this is for you.

574
00:34:24,080 --> 00:34:26,619
You can use it to make soup or steep it in water.

575
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:28,459
You seem very tired lately.

576
00:34:28,459 --> 00:34:30,160
Make sure you stay healthy.

577
00:34:34,900 --> 00:34:36,480
Caterpillar fungus?

578
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:38,059
There's no need to thank me. You can just treat me to a meal.

579
00:34:38,059 --> 00:34:40,200
No, I can't accept this. It's too expensive. I can't afford it.

580
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:41,899
It's cheap. Take it.

581
00:34:41,899 --> 00:34:44,539
Thank you for your concern. I'll buy you a meal next time.

582
00:34:44,539 --> 00:34:47,439
Today, Xiao Hu Lu's dad is coming to visit here. I have to go home.

583
00:34:47,439 --> 00:34:49,100
Aunty Baoping.

584
00:34:49,100 --> 00:34:51,419
A'Hui is following her everywhere.

585
00:34:51,420 --> 00:34:53,480
Keep it down.

586
00:34:54,660 --> 00:34:57,959
Stop following me around. I won't accept this.

587
00:34:57,959 --> 00:35:00,399
I traveled very far to get this for you.

588
00:35:00,399 --> 00:35:02,340
- Take it.
- Bring it home. Give it to your family.

589
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:04,139
Take it. It's good for your health.

590
00:35:04,140 --> 00:35:06,320
I'll help you. I'll carry it for you.

591
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:17,320
It's time to eat.

592
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:20,240
- I'll bring the dishes out.
- No, it's fine.

593
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:22,699
Take a seat. Xiao Hu Lu, take a break. Clear the table.

594
00:35:22,699 --> 00:35:24,880
Let's eat first. Dad will help you pack.

595
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:27,440
Sure. Wash your hands.

596
00:35:30,060 --> 00:35:31,600
You must be hungry, Luo Quan.

597
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:33,500
Mom, I'm not hungry.

598
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:34,699
You must be starving.

599
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:35,819
Goodness.

600
00:35:35,820 --> 00:35:37,859
The company has new regulations now.

601
00:35:37,859 --> 00:35:41,259
If we don't clock in or out on time, we can't get the attendance bonus.

602
00:35:41,259 --> 00:35:43,699
- You must've been waiting.
- It's fine.

603
00:35:43,699 --> 00:35:46,060
It's nice to watch Xiao Hu Lu practice writing.

604
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:48,680
Well, take a seat.

605
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:50,759
What about Xia Xia?

606
00:35:50,759 --> 00:35:52,820
Xiaxia doesn't eat at home.

607
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:54,820
Here you go.

608
00:35:57,380 --> 00:35:58,299
Thank you, Mom.

609
00:35:58,300 --> 00:36:00,240
Pass me her bowl.

610
00:36:01,380 --> 00:36:05,480
How are the sales of water purifiers recently?

611
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:06,399
Not bad.

612
00:36:06,399 --> 00:36:09,440
- Not bad?
- That's good.

613
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:12,799
How are your parents? Are they well?

614
00:36:12,799 --> 00:36:14,059
They're getting by fine.

615
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:14,779
That's good.

616
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:16,579
You... should hurry up and eat.

617
00:36:16,580 --> 00:36:20,299
Head back early. It'll be dangerous to drive at night.

618
00:36:20,299 --> 00:36:21,820
Okay.

619
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:25,780
Have you told your parents

620
00:36:25,780 --> 00:36:28,240
about Xiao Hu Lu attending elementary school?

621
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:33,979
Well... That's not urgent.

622
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:41,400
You can't be so lax about everything.

623
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:45,419
Your parents assume Xiao Hu Lu will study in Kunming.

624
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:47,159
You have to tell them immediately.

625
00:36:47,159 --> 00:36:49,019
You can't leave everything to a later date.

626
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:51,540
Listen up. I hate this aspect of you the most.

627
00:36:52,780 --> 00:36:54,099
Eat.

628
00:36:54,099 --> 00:36:57,080
I know. I'll tell them when I get back.

629
00:36:58,420 --> 00:37:00,720
- Eat.
- Thank you, Mom.

630
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:03,199
You must tell them, okay?

631
00:37:03,199 --> 00:37:05,440
I will. Here you go.

632
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:07,880
- Mom, have some of this.
- I can take it myself.

633
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:10,919
Stop bothering with others. Eat more meat.

634
00:37:22,540 --> 00:37:24,140
Here.

635
00:37:24,140 --> 00:37:27,760
These are for your parents.

636
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:31,920
Remember to tell them that Xiao Hu Lu is studying here.

637
00:37:33,340 --> 00:37:37,360
Also... do you have enough money?

638
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:40,940
We're saving for Xiao Hu Lu's education,

639
00:37:40,940 --> 00:37:43,459
but selling water purifiers isn't a stable job.

640
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:45,720
If you're struggling, tell me.

641
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:48,540
I eat at home, so I don't need much money.

642
00:37:48,540 --> 00:37:50,499
I see. Take care of yourself.

643
00:37:50,499 --> 00:37:53,660
I won't use any money from Xiao Hu Lu's bank account.

644
00:37:53,660 --> 00:37:55,220
Get going.

645
00:37:55,660 --> 00:37:57,300
Xiaochun.

646
00:38:00,700 --> 00:38:03,300
Cut to the chase.

647
00:38:05,020 --> 00:38:07,620
Are you in a relationship?

648
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:12,999
Hold on. Why are you asking about this?

649
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,400
Focus on yourself.

650
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:18,280
Besides, I'll take care of our daughter no matter what happens.

651
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:20,199
I-I didn't mean that.

652
00:38:20,199 --> 00:38:21,699
One more thing, Luo Quan.

653
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:23,059
I don't care if you date someone,

654
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:26,179
but you have to make things clear to your mom. Don't beat around the bush all the time.

655
00:38:26,179 --> 00:38:29,859
She calls my mom whenever she gets anxious, and my mom has to console her.

656
00:38:29,859 --> 00:38:32,139
You're an inexplicable guy.

657
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:35,679
Why can't you call me when there are problems? Why do you call my mom?

658
00:38:35,679 --> 00:38:37,659
What are you guys even thinking?

659
00:38:37,660 --> 00:38:40,620
I want to call you,

660
00:38:40,620 --> 00:38:43,779
but I... I'm afraid of your berating.

661
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:46,960
When have I done that?

662
00:38:50,500 --> 00:38:52,459
Fine, get going.

663
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:54,340
Drive carefully.

664
00:38:59,380 --> 00:39:01,380
I'll visit again next month.

665
00:39:01,380 --> 00:39:03,459
You don't have to come over if you're busy.

666
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:07,240
I'll ask Xiao Hu Lu to visit her grandparents during the holidays.

667
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:09,160
I'll come next month.

668
00:39:09,160 --> 00:39:11,120
Well, do what you like.

669
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:14,819
Xiaochun, can't you be more patient with me?

670
00:39:14,820 --> 00:39:18,119
Haven't I been patient with you? Mr. Bow Legs.

671
00:39:18,119 --> 00:39:19,480
Listen to you. You're insulting me again!

672
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,419
Look at yourself! You have bow legs!

673
00:39:21,419 --> 00:39:22,840
I...

674
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:27,279
Your parents gave you the perfect name.

675
00:39:27,279 --> 00:39:30,020
You grew up to fit your name.

676
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:36,640
All right, enough. Get going.

677
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:38,020
I'll head off.

678
00:39:38,020 --> 00:39:40,060
I'll come next month.

679
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:49,020
Xiaochun.

680
00:39:49,020 --> 00:39:52,020
Can you please say everything once?

681
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:54,459
Take care.

682
00:39:54,460 --> 00:39:56,480
Don't work too hard.

683
00:39:59,060 --> 00:40:01,620
- I'm leaving.
- Get going.

684
00:40:14,220 --> 00:40:17,560
Look at him. How could I have fallen for him in university?

685
00:40:26,460 --> 00:40:27,720
Come on. Be careful. I'll carry it.

686
00:40:27,720 --> 00:40:29,240
Okay.

687
00:40:29,780 --> 00:40:31,940
Take it easy.

688
00:40:34,220 --> 00:40:35,939
Why is there so much soil on them?

689
00:40:35,940 --> 00:40:39,400
Sister Xiaochun, it's impossible to be entirely clean of soil.

690
00:40:40,060 --> 00:40:43,380
- 61. Take note next time.
- Of course.

691
00:40:43,380 --> 00:40:46,479
One, two, three! Come on.

692
00:40:46,479 --> 00:40:49,020
Guys! Xiaoyue, bring these in.

693
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:54,940
In my opinion, A'Hui is a decent guy.

694
00:40:54,940 --> 00:40:57,259
His house is so lavish.

695
00:40:57,260 --> 00:41:00,720
I even heard that he has another house in Xiaguan.

696
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:02,120
Baoping.

697
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:04,820
It's fine even if he's a little younger.

698
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:07,879
You think A'Hui is decent, but Xiaochun doesn't like him.

699
00:41:07,879 --> 00:41:09,999
Xiao Hu Lu's dad visits all the time.

700
00:41:09,999 --> 00:41:12,219
Are they back together now?

701
00:41:12,220 --> 00:41:16,180
Luo Quan doesn't even talk properly.

702
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:18,200
I realized ages ago.

703
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:20,460
He's a poor match for Xiaochun.

704
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:22,099
In what sense?

705
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:24,019
A short fuse with a silent pot.

706
00:41:24,019 --> 00:41:27,219
If both of them have short fuses, their lives would be hell.

707
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:28,759
- Don't you agree?
- Exactly.

708
00:41:28,759 --> 00:41:30,380
- Yeah.
- That's true.

709
00:41:30,380 --> 00:41:32,340
Good evening.

710
00:41:33,020 --> 00:41:34,059
Hongdou's here.

711
00:41:34,060 --> 00:41:35,360
Aunty A'Gui, you're here too.

712
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:37,539
I'll just watch television at home.

713
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:38,979
It's better to hang out with them here.

714
00:41:38,980 --> 00:41:41,419
- I'm helping out too.
- That's nice.

715
00:41:41,419 --> 00:41:42,539
Why are you here?

716
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:45,739
We're packing potatoes for distribution. It's dirty here.

717
00:41:45,740 --> 00:41:47,099
I'm here to help.

718
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:49,740
What? Do you think I'm a nuisance?

719
00:41:50,480 --> 00:41:52,199
How dare he?

720
00:41:52,199 --> 00:41:54,019
He's dying to meet you.

721
00:41:54,020 --> 00:41:56,219
He's so happy that you're here.

722
00:41:56,220 --> 00:41:58,619
She's here to help. Don't tease her.

723
00:41:58,620 --> 00:41:59,960
Exactly.

724
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:03,219
A'Yao and Hongdou haven't even made things official,

725
00:42:03,219 --> 00:42:06,860
but you're already waiting for a wedding party.

726
00:42:08,020 --> 00:42:10,680
Well, what can I help with?

727
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:12,560
Sit here.

728
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:13,979
Stick on the delivery slips with me.

729
00:42:13,980 --> 00:42:15,420
How do I do it?

730
00:42:15,420 --> 00:42:16,420
I'll teach you. Look.

731
00:42:16,420 --> 00:42:18,219
Stick these labels stating five kilograms on the small boxes.

732
00:42:18,220 --> 00:42:20,980
The labels for ten kilograms go on the large boxes.

733
00:42:21,460 --> 00:42:22,900
I'll take this down.

734
00:42:22,900 --> 00:42:24,380
<i>Okay.</i>

735
00:42:24,380 --> 00:42:26,900
What were you guys chatting about?

736
00:42:26,900 --> 00:42:31,320
We were talking about Xiaochun.

737
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:33,739
Xiao Hu Lu's dad visits often.

738
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:36,239
A'Hui, the supplier, likes her too.

739
00:42:36,239 --> 00:42:39,019
Xiaochun doesn't feel anything toward them.

740
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:41,260
She doesn't care about either one.

741
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:44,440
When did Xiao Hu Lu's dad come back?

742
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:46,259
It's their divorce agreement.

743
00:42:46,260 --> 00:42:47,539
He can visit the child once a month.

744
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:50,200
So, Luo Quan comes over every month.

745
00:42:50,780 --> 00:42:51,939
Why did they get a divorce?

746
00:42:51,940 --> 00:42:53,780
He never came home.

747
00:42:54,300 --> 00:42:55,820
Was he having an affair?

748
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:59,379
Nope. He's selling water purifiers.

749
00:42:59,379 --> 00:43:02,799
Youngsters these days get a divorce after a small bump.

750
00:43:02,799 --> 00:43:05,420
Do you know Xiao Bai living in the courtyard?

751
00:43:05,420 --> 00:43:08,940
Her child is already in university, but she still got a divorce.

752
00:43:08,940 --> 00:43:13,539
Hear this. I saw Xiao Bai hanging out with Hu Youyu.

753
00:43:13,540 --> 00:43:16,100
They're at the bar every day.

754
00:43:16,100 --> 00:43:17,899
Why does she see in him?

755
00:43:17,900 --> 00:43:19,259
What does she want from him?

756
00:43:19,260 --> 00:43:22,379
Mr. Hu is a talented musician.

757
00:43:22,380 --> 00:43:24,859
Girls love such charming men.

758
00:43:24,860 --> 00:43:26,619
What kind of charm does he have?

759
00:43:26,620 --> 00:43:28,299
He has such a glib tongue.

760
00:43:28,300 --> 00:43:32,300
I should warn Xiao Bai or she'll be duped.

761
00:43:32,300 --> 00:43:33,659
Stop it.

762
00:43:33,660 --> 00:43:35,680
Don't be so nosy.

763
00:43:35,680 --> 00:43:37,819
You're just prejudiced against Mr. Hu.

764
00:43:37,820 --> 00:43:39,880
He's a nice person.

765
00:43:40,540 --> 00:43:43,219
He just expresses himself in an annoying way,

766
00:43:43,220 --> 00:43:44,779
but he's really loyal.

767
00:43:44,780 --> 00:43:46,240
He's very caring to his friends.

768
00:43:46,240 --> 00:43:48,659
You can't judge a book by its cover.

769
00:43:48,660 --> 00:43:51,240
You should get to know him better.

770
00:43:51,900 --> 00:43:54,119
Are his parents still around?

771
00:43:54,119 --> 00:43:56,399
They are. Even his grandparents are doing well.

772
00:43:56,399 --> 00:44:00,760
Since he's so caring, why doesn't he go home?

773
00:44:02,300 --> 00:44:06,520
You guys shouldn't judge a book by its cover!

774
00:44:06,520 --> 00:44:08,900
Right, Baoping?

775
00:44:16,540 --> 00:44:18,220
Mr. Hu.

776
00:44:22,500 --> 00:44:25,519
Okay. I'll be there right away. Wait for me.

777
00:44:25,519 --> 00:44:26,580
What's going on?

778
00:44:26,580 --> 00:44:28,139
I have to go to the bar.

779
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:30,300
